verbose_text: Functionally, knockdown of CXCR2 significantly inhibited the cell proliferation rate by 33% (P < 0.0001) but did not alter the capacities of ovarian cancer cells in anchorage independent growth (P = 0.35), migration (P = 0.20), and invasion (P = 0.37).
evidence: CXCR2 significantly inhibited the cell proliferation
